skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: office workout
des:
Exercise is perceived to be the most painful thing any human can do then it is made to be serious and boring or People just don't know what exercise to do! So this skill aims to solve these issues.. Ok Sorta solve these issues. Exercise will still be no walk in the park but I have tried to make it as fun as possible while maintaining 'recommended' exercises for the office. Enough Waffle. Lets get started! All you need to do is invoke the skill whenever you have a breather. This version is being expanded with more exercises as its age goes on. I hope you enjoy using it. If you have any suggestions or exercise ideas email me (anushpatel0@gmail.com)! 

Anush

<-- Planned Updates -->
I plan to add some nice music to the skill but I have opposed it so far as I have a feeling people in the office don't ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
I am adding a more diverse set of activities and improving the jokes 
Once Amazon allows to : Set reminders for you and send notifications to your devices!

<-- Disclaimer -->
Anush Patel (The Developer) is not responsible for any injuries caused by using the skill. This skill is to be used for guidance purposes only. If you feel that the activity is unsafe then skip it. These Activities have been created with the use of NHS and other medical agency exercises. If in doubt warm up.
